cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.GT, cs.SI, cs.CE 

This paper discusses the application of economic and pricing models for resource management in 5G wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses spectrum allocation and interference management, which are related to information theory (cs.IT). Game theory (cs.GT) is also mentioned as a tool for resource management. The paper also discusses the use of caching, which falls under the category of signal processing (cs.SI) and mobile data offloading, which is related to computer engineering (cs.CE).
